Title: Fjallraven ABISKO TRAIL T-SHIRT
Description: The practical and easily cared for garment is suitable for trekking and travelling in warm climates, where the wool transports moisture away from the body and resists bad odours, while the tencel makes the garment drape well and feels comfortable against the skin. The Abisko Trail T-Shirt Print by FJALLRAVEN convinces with its round neck, attractive raglan sleeves and the slightly longer back.On the front of the Abisko Trail T - Shirt Print by FJALLRAVEN for men there is a FJALLRAVEN logo print and the narrow, flatlock seams minimise the risk of chafing.
